 Jeremy Trentelman , 36 , of Ogden , last week built a giant box fort for his three-year-old son Max and two daughter Story , that included trap doors and a small slide .
The father , who works as a florist arranging intricate displays was greeted with a letter from code enforcement city officials saying that his creation must be scrapped .
Trentelman has decided to leave it for the maximum two weeks before a fine .